Package: ols
Title: REST API Client for the Ontology Lookup Service
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ramiro", "Magno", , "rmagno@pattern.institute", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5226-3441")),
    person("Pattern Institute", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Programmatic access to the Ontology Lookup Service (OLS).
    This package provides easy access to biomedical ontologies as made available
    by the European Bioinformatics Institute 'OLS' through its REST API
    <https://www.ebi.ac.uk/ols4/api/ontologies>.
